    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The chassis remains structurally flawless, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension setup that retains its factory-spec damping and bushing compliance. Power is managed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, feeding a limited-slip differential for exceptional lateral grip. The exterior factory finish is unblemished, and the interior maintains its original Nappa leather integrity with no bolster wear or UV degradation. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
